Package: officerWinTools
Title: Functions to compliment 'officer' R package using Microsoft Office in a Windows environment
Version: 0.1.1
Enhances:
    officer
Imports:
    officer, 
    R.utils
Suggests:
    dplyr
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joshua",
           family = "Mire",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "the.doctor@joshmire.com")
Description: THIS PACKAGE REQUIRES A WINDOWS OPERATING SYSTEM AND MICROSOFT 
    OFFICE.  The package is meant to be used along side the 'officer' package.  
    The package includes functions for exporting Microsoft Word and PowerPoint 
    files as .pdf files.  The package also includes a function for updating the 
    tables of contents of a Microsoft Word document created with 'officer'.  
    Exporting Microsoft Word documents automatically updates all Tables of 
    Contents and hyperlinks their page numbers.
